OL,5, A 13-year-old boy died after being     
OL,6, deliberately pushed into a river in a  
OL,7, "dangerous prank", a coroner has ruled.
OL,9,FChristopher Kapessa drowned after      
OL,10,Fgetting into difficulty in the River   
OL,11,FCynon near Fernhill, Rhondda Cynon Taf,
OL,12,Fin July 2019.                          
OL,14,FCoroner David Regan said evidence from 
OL,15,FJayden Pugh, who said he slipped and   
OL,16,Ffell into Christopher, was "untrue".   
OL,18,FBut Christopher's mother said the      
OL,19,Finjustice she believed her family had  
OL,20,Fendured "haunted" her.                 
